      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "I guess most GUI users don't use the RPC interface and it's unclear to me if it is worth to enable it by default for better integration with HWI/junction.\r\n\r\nThough better GUI integration **to enable the RPC interface** would be desirable IMO. Maybe a setting that could directly enable the interface without a restart (yes, needs some refactoring)...",
